Package: RosettaCOTS
Type: Package
Title: Calbration and Translation tool for COTS and Coral measurement tools
Version: 1.0.2
Authors@R: c(person("Scott", "Foster", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                     email = "scott.foster@data61.csiro.au"))
Maintainer: Scott Foseter <scott.foster@data61.csiro.au>
Depends: 
  R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
  methods,
  stats
Suggests:
  rjags,
  readxl
VignetteBuilder: knitr, rmarkdown
Description: Predicts measurements from one type of sampling tool (e.g. Manta Tows) to another type (e.g. Cull dives). The range of COTS measurement tools are: Cull dives, SALAD dives, eDNA (concentration), eDNA (proportion). The range of Scar measurement tools are: Manta Tows, SALAD. The range of Coral cover measurement tools are: Manta Tows, ReefScan-transom, ReefScan-Deep, Transect (from SALAD dives).
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
